description:
Explore and navigate the world with confidence using Google Maps. Find the best routes with live traffic data and real-time GPS navigation for driving, walking, cycling and public transport. Discover over 250 million businesses and places – from restaurants and shops to everyday essentials – with photos, reviews and helpful information.

Navigate the world, the way that you want:
• Get to where you need to go with fuel-efficient route options
• Find the best route with real-time, turn-by-turn voice and on-screen navigation
• Save time with automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Catch the bus, train and ride-share effortlessly, with real-time updates
• Find bike or scooter rentals to get around more easily

Plan trips and experiences effortlessly:
• Preview an area before you go (e.g. parking, entrances) with Street View
• Use Immersive View to experience what landmarks, parks and routes look like, and even check the weather so that you can be ready in advance
• Create custom lists of your favourite saved places and share with others
• Order delivery and takeaway, make reservations and book hotels
• Don't get lost with offline maps in an area with bad signal
• Search for local places and things to do, and decide based on user reviews and photos

Discover and explore like a local:
• Explore with confidence knowing 500 million users contribute and keep the map up to date each year
• Avoid the crowds by seeing how busy a place is before you get there
• Use Lens in Maps to see walking directions overlaid on the real world
• Filter restaurants by cuisine, hours, price, rating and more
• Ask questions about a place, from dishes to parking, and get quick answers

Some features not available in all countries or cities
Navigation isn't intended to be used by oversized or emergency vehicles

Moovit is one app for all your urban mobility and transport rides!

Dailymail - "This travel app is a godsend for anyone using public transport – with live updates to bus schedules, as well as a great route-planner for cities across the UK."

Transportation is an integral part of urban living. Whether you ride the train, subway/underground /tube, bus, light rail, ferry or metro, use bikes, ride-sharing like Uber, getting the best urban mobility information is critical. Moovit guides you from point A to B in the easiest and most efficient way. Get train and bus times, maps, and live arrival times with ease so you can plan your trip with confidence. Find critical alerts and service disruptions for your favorite lines. Get step-by-step directions of optimal route bus, train, metro, bike or a combination of them. 
This is why Moovit has been named one of the best apps of the year 2017 by the App Store!

Moovit guides more than 865 million users in over 3200 cities throughout the world.

► Journey Planner that combines you all transport options and gives you the best route with live arrivals.

► Live Directions: Get step-by-step directions with live guidance as you travel: know exactly how long you need to walk to your station, how long you’re waiting, view the arrival time of your line and how many stops are left. 

► Real time arrivals. View real-time arrival updates, which are taken directly from GPS devices positioned on buses and trains.

► Real time alerts. Know about issues ahead of time by receiving service alerts such as emergency or unexpected disruptions, delays, traffic jams, new construction and more...

► Users reports. Moovit’s users report issues found with stations, line service, and timetables so that we can inform all nearby riders about what’s going on in their area.

► Favorite lines, stations, and places. Get easy access to lines, stations, and places you ride and visit all the time. Plus, get real-time updates if/when there are changes to your favorite lines in case your bus or train time is impacted!

► Bike routes. Get bike routes in addition to the bus, subway, train, or metro trip plans. If you ride bikes (yours or shared) we can plan a route that includes the train or bus. 
Bike docking stations are updated in real-time.

► Maps view. View all stations, routes, and lines on the subway or bus map. Additionally, maps are available in PDF for when you’re offline, or underground on the subway. 

Ride with Moovit in all major cities:

UK:
• London
• Manchester
• Birmingham
• Leeds
• Edinburgh
• Glasgow
• Liverpool
• Sheffield

Ireland:
• Dublin and all of the Republic of Ireland.

•Mumbai: Mumbai Metro (M.M.R.D.A), all buses: BEST, NMMT, KDMT, VVMT, MBMT, KMT, TMT, Ferries and more

You ride, we guide!

developer: DIRECT CURSUS COMPUTER SYSTEMS TRADING LLC
description:
Yandex Navigator is the perfect companion for drivers.
It helps you find your way around the city with fast, convenient directions that avoid traffic jams and road closures. If road conditions change, Yandex Navigator adjusts your route on the fly.

No surprises on the road
Get detailed directions as you drive and find out about road conditions ahead of time. The app warns you about traffic, speed limits, cameras, and road closures. 
It also lets you know when there’s an upcoming turn or complex intersection. And since it does that using voice notifications, you can keep your eyes on the road.

Get multi-stop directions
There’s no need to waste time planning the most efficient routes if you need to make multiple stops along the way. Let Yandex Navigator do the work for you.
Plan a route with 4-10 stops and tap "Optimize." Yandex Navigator will reorder them to make the route as quick and convenient as possible.

Get your bearings anywhere 
No matter where you are, Yandex Navigator shows you how to get to where you need to go. Search for restaurants, cafes, bars, shops, gas stations, pharmacies, stadiums, law firms, or anything else, navigating there quickly and stress-free.

Never get lost offline
Find places and plan routes even without a connection once you’ve downloaded offline maps for your city or region.

Pay for parking 
Look for convenient parking spots near your destination. And since you can pay for them right from Yandex Navigator, you don’t need other apps.

Pay for fuel
Choose your fuel type, select how much you need, and pay for it without leaving the app. Just tap the fuel tank button, and you'll see all nearby gas stations along with their available payment options.

Steer clear of poor road conditions
Turn on "Avoid bad and unpaved roads" in the route parameters or app settings. Yandex Navigator will guide you along smooth, paved roads wherever possible.

Plan your trips ahead of time
Adjust departure date and time settings to see how long your route is in advance.
For example, you can plan how to get to the airport the evening before your flight by setting the departure date for the next day. Yandex Navigator shows how long it usually takes to drive that route at that time, taking into account the usual traffic conditions. You'll definitely get there on schedule.

Get directions tailored to your vehicle
If you're driving a truck or other freight vehicle, select "Add truck" in the app settings and describe your vehicle's characteristics. Yandex Navigator will get directions that account for any weight, size, or emission limitations.

Monitor traffic in real time
Yandex Navigator updates your route details when traffic conditions change. You can also add widgets to your phone’s home screen that show traffic levels for your favorite routes so you can keep track of them even without  opening the app.

See your route laid out in front of you 
Yandex Navigator is available for CarPlay, making it easy to follow your route on the screen in front of you without getting distracted by your phone. To make that work, you'll need a Yandex Plus subscription.

The app works in Russia, Abkhazia, Azerbaijan, Armenia, Belarus, Georgia, Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan, Moldova, Tajikistan, Turkey, Uzbekistan.

The only app that combines real time alerts with the best offline radar detection alert system. With Radarbot, you will have the best radar alerts, real time traffic alerts and specific speed limit alerts for different vehicles (cars, motorbikes, trucks and commercial vehicles) in one powerful app. Focus on what really matters while driving and enjoy your journey.

With Radarbot, drive more peacefully. Safer. Better.

SPEED CAMERA WARNINGS
Enjoy driving without having to worry about risking your safety or driving licence. Avoid traffic fines and penalties by receiving clear warnings before passing speed cameras:

- Fixed speed cameras.
- Possible mobile speed cameras (frequent areas).
- Tunnel speed cameras.
- Average speed cameras (the app displays the average speed).
- Traffic light cameras.

Plus:
- Dangerous driving areas.
- Seat belt or cell phone use cameras.
- Restricted area access control cameras.
- Potholes and speed bumps on the road.

* FEATURES:
- Works in any country.
- Compatible with other apps. You can use Radarbot together with other GPS navigators or your favourite music app. You will still receive alerts in the background or while the screen is turned off.
- Alerts only in the direction you are driving. The app automatically ignores speed cameras for traffic going in the opposite direction or off route.
- Voice alerts.
- Sound alerts when approaching a speed camera or going over the speed limit.
- Vibration mode for motorists.
- Fully configurable warning distances and parameters.
- Automatic Bluetooth connection and startup.
- Compatible with Apple Watch.

REAL TIME ALERTS
Real time alerts will warn you of any unexpected circumstances. Radarbot has a community of over 50 million drivers worldwide with whom you can share and receive alerts. Find out immediately what is happening on the road and avoid traffic jams, hazards, accidents, mobile speed cameras, police, helicopters, drones, and much more.

SPEED CAMERA UPDATE
Radarbot has the most powerful, up-to-date speed camera database in the world. Our team of experts perform daily updates to ensure that the database always contains the very latest information. Not a single speed camera can escape the prying eyes of Radarbot!

RADARBOT WORLDWIDE
Try our totally "FREE" version for as long as you like. If you want to get the full experience, you can try "Radarbot GOLD" and "Radarbot GOLD RoadPro" with integrated GPS navigation, unique advantages and, of course, no advertising.

GPS NAVIGATION AND SPEED LIMITS
Discover the power of Radarbot. The GOLD version offers everything you need on the road in a single app: GPS navigation, speed cameras and speed limits. Even if you don't have an internet connection, you will still arrive safe and sound at your destination. Get speed camera alerts wherever you are in the world without having to worry about using up your mobile data.

Where would you like to go?

* FEATURES:
- Offline navigation and 3D maps.
- Possibility of choosing a route with fewer speed cameras.
- Road speed limits.
- Alerts for school areas and associated speed cameras.
- Radarbot co-pilot. Put your seat belt on!

ARE YOU A PROFESSIONAL DRIVER?
"Radarbot GOLD RoadPro" includes everything a professional driver could need:

- Routes with special restrictions for lorries and commercial vehicles.
- Speed limits and specific speed cameras for lorries.
- Distance alerts adapted to heavy vehicles.

If you have any doubts or queries, we would be more than happy for you to get in touch with us at radarbot@iteration-mobile.com or by using the customer support option inside the app.

Download Radarbot now and become a member of the "Enjoy driving!" movement.

* Continuous use of GPS in the background can drastically reduce battery life.

developer: Ankara Buyuksehir Belediyesi Ego Genel Mudurlugu
description:
EGO CEP'TE application, which allows the tracking of EGO Buses, Private Public Buses (ÖHO) and Private Public Transport Vehicles (ÖTA), of the EGO General Directorate, is at the service of the people of Ankara with its new face. The application, with its user-friendly new design and simple and fast structure, gives users the opportunity to reach what they are looking for much more easily.

• “Where is the Bus?” on the main page. With its feature, it is possible to learn very quickly when the relevant line bus will arrive at the called stop with a 5-digit stop number. Favorited stops “Where is the Bus?” automatically appears under the feature. Buses approaching the station can also be viewed on the map.

• Line announcements and important developments published by the EGO General Directorate are listed and can be accessed in detail upon request.

• Search can be made with the 5-digit stop number or the name of the stop, and the buses of all lines passing through the relevant stop can be displayed. If location permission is granted, nearby stops can be listed and displayed on the map.

• All EGO, ÖHO and ÖTA bus lines serving in Ankara can be viewed with their stops, times, vehicles serving at that time and their routes. In addition, basic information of Metro, Ankaray and Suburban lines can be accessed.

• With the application, all Ankarakart Dealers or only those nearby can be listed and displayed on the map. In addition, the balance and usage history of the added Ankarakart can be viewed and the balance can be loaded.

• Lines and stops that are frequently used by users are added to favorites so that they can be followed more easily.

• With Başkent 153 integration, an application can be created quickly for suggestions, requests or complaints for transportation services.

developer: Esarj Elektrikli Araclar Sarj Sistemleri A.S.
description: The new mobile application of the first EV charging network operator in Türkiye with the highest number of DC stations, Eşarj.

Know what's ahead on the road with the help from other drivers. Waze is a live map that harnesses the local knowledge of tens of millions of drivers around the world. Drivers safely and confidently reach their everyday destinations thanks to Waze map’s GPS navigation, live traffic updates, real-time safety alerts (including roadworks, accidents, crashes, police, potholes and more) and accurate ETAs.


Make your next drive more predictable and stress-free:
• Get there faster with real-time directions, accurate ETAs and automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Even if you know the way, avoid surprises on the road ahead with safety alerts for accidents, crashes, roadworks, objects on the road, potholes, speed bumps, sharp curves, bad weather, emergency vehicles, railway crossings and more
• Steer clear of tickets by knowing where police and red light and speed cameras are located
• Share what’s happening on the road with other drivers by reporting live incidents and hazards
• Stay informed of upcoming speed limit changes, and keep your speedometer in check
• Know which lane to be in with multi-lane guidance
• See toll pricing and choose to avoid tolls along your routes
• Add road passes and vignettes for HOV lanes and restricted traffic zones
• Find petrol/fuel stations and prices and EV charging stations along your route
• Locate car parks near your destination
• Use voice-guided turn-by-turn navigation from a variety of languages, local accents and your favourite celebrities
• Plan your next drive by checking ETAs by future departure or arrival times
• Use your favourite audio apps (for podcasts, music, news, audiobooks) directly within Waze
• Sync Waze to your car’s built-in display through Apple CarPlay


* Some features are not available in all countries


* Waze navigation is not intended for emergency or oversized vehicles


You can manage your in-app Waze privacy settings at any time. Learn more about the Waze privacy policy here, www.waze.com/legal/privacy.

developer: BORUSAN OTOMOTIV ITHALAT VE DAGITIM ANONIM SIRKETI
description:
Tüm elektrikli araçlar için en yakın ve en uygun şarj istasyonunu harita üzerinden anında bul!


ChargeIQ, Türkiye’nin en kapsamlı elektrikli şarj istasyonu haritasını sunar. Uygulama ile istasyonları canlı takip edin, rotanızı oluşturun, doluluk ve tarife bilgilerini anlık karşılaştırın. Yolda şarj aramakla vakit kaybetmeyin – ChargeIQ ile şarjsız kalmayın!

Borusan Otomotiv’in sürdürülebilirlik vizyonuyla geliştirilen ChargeIQ, tüm şarj sağlayıcıları, soket tipleri, fiyat tarifeleri ve konum bilgilerini tek bir platformda sunarak sürücü deneyimini en üst düzeye çıkarır.

• Tüm Elektrikli Araçlarla Uyumlu
Porsche Taycan, Tesla (S, 3, X, Y), BMW (i4, i5, i7, iX, iX1), MINI, Renault ZOE, Jaguar I-PACE, Fiat 500e, Kia EV6, Togg T10X, Hyundai IONIQ, Skywell, Megane e-Tech, Volvo, MG, Peugeot (E-208, E-3008, E-5008) ve diğer tüm elektrikli araçlarla uyumludur.

• Tek Platformda Tüm Şarj Sağlayıcılar
ZES, E-şarj, Trugo, SharzNet, Voltrun, Borenco, Tora, WAT, Astor ve daha fazlası ChargeIQ’da bir arada!

- Öne Çıkan Özellikler

• Şarj İstasyonları Haritası:
Türkiye genelindeki AC/DC istasyonları gelişmiş harita ile anında keşfedin. Konum, uzaklık, puan ve doluluk bilgilerini görün.

• Navigasyon ve Rota Planlama:
Başlangıç ve varış noktalarınızı girerek yolculuğunuza en uygun rotayı oluşturun. Yol üzerindeki istasyonları görüntüleyin ve rotayı kaydederek navigasyonu başlatın.

• Gerçek Zamanlı Durum Bilgisi:
İstasyonlardaki şarj cihazlarının doluluk ve soket uygunluk bilgilerini canlı olarak takip edin. Check-in özelliğiyle istasyon kullanımını bildirip topluluğa katkı sağlayın.

• Gelişmiş Filtreleme:
İstasyonları; operatör, soket tipi (AC/DC), kW gücü, şarj ağı, istasyon puanı, tarife tipi, yeşil enerji seçeneği ve lokasyona göre filtreleyerek kolayca bulun.

• Tarife ve Maliyet Hesaplama:
İstasyon fiyatlarını karşılaştırın. Aracınıza özel şarj süresi ve maliyet hesaplamasını yaparak yolculuğunuzu önceden planlayın.

• Favori Şarj Noktaları:
Sık kullandığınız ya da beğendiğiniz şarj istasyonlarını favorilere ekleyin, daha sonra kolayca erişin.

• Topluluk Desteği ve Sürdürülebilirlik:
Kullanıcı yorumları, değerlendirmeler ve fotoğraflarla en güvenilir şarj noktalarını keşfedin. Siz de deneyimlerinizi paylaşarak katkı sağlayın.

• Araç ve Profil Yönetimi:
Araç bilgilerinizi (model, plaka, menzil, soket tipi) uygulamaya kaydedin. Şarj geçmişinizi inceleyin, tüketim verilerinizi analiz edin.

• Keşfet Sekmesi:
Elektrikli araç dünyasına dair yazılar, sürdürülebilirlik içerikleri ve yolculuk ipuçları ile bilgi dolu bir keşif alanı.

• Cebinizdeki Akıllı Şarj Asistanı:
İster şehir içinde ister uzun yolda olun, ihtiyaç duyduğunuz tüm şarj bilgileri tek uygulamada! Şarj istasyonu bulma, tarifeleri karşılaştırma ve rota planlama artık çok kolay.

- ChargeIQ ile Neler Yapabilirsiniz?

• Size en yakın şarj istasyonunu bulun
• Şarj cihazı doluluk durumunu kontrol edin
• Şarj süresi ve maliyetini hesaplayın
• Rota oluşturun ve navigasyonu başlatın
• Favori noktalarınızı ekleyin
• İstasyonlara puan verin ve yorum yapın
• Topluluk deneyimlerinden yararlanın
• Soket tipi, güç, tarife gibi detaylara göre filtreleme yapın
• Gerçek zamanlı fiyat ve enerji bilgilerini inceleyin

Şarj istasyonu bulmak, yolculuk planlamak ve elektrikli araç kullanımını kolaylaştırmak için ChargeIQ’yu hemen indir!

developer: Voltla Elektrikli Araclar Bilisim Reklam ve Tanitim Hizmetleri Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
description:
Voltla; Togg, Tesla, Bmw, Mercedes, Volvo, MG, Skywell, Peugeot, Opel gibi elektrikli araç sahipleri için tüm şarj istasyonlarını bulma, araç şarj fiyatlarını tek noktadan öğrenme, şarj istasyonlarına rota oluşturma ve şarj & ödeme başlatma uygulamasıdır.

Elektrikli araçların yaygınlaşması ile birlikte, kullanıcıların kolayca erişebilecekleri güvenilir & hızlı şarj istasyonlarına olan ihtiyaç artmıştır. Voltla bu ihtiyacı karşılamak için tasarlanmış, geniş kapsamlı bir şarj istasyonları haritası çözümüdür. 

Voltla’da, e şarj ağı firmaları ile Voltla; Togg, Tesla, Bmw, Mercedes, Volvo, MG, Skywell, Peugeot, Opel gibi elektrikli araç sahiplerini bir araya getiriyor, kullanıcıların ihtiyaçlarına en uygun şarj istasyonunu bulmalarını ve bu istasyonlara en hızlı şekilde ulaşmalarını sağlıyoruz. Zes, Eşarj, Trugo gibi tüm şarj istasyonlarının bilgilerini de Voltla içinden kolaylıkla görebilir ve markaları karşılaştırabilirsiniz.

Özellikler:

Elektrikli Araç Şarj İstasyonları Haritası: Kullanıcıların bulundukları konuma en yakın şarj istasyonlarını hızlıca bulmalarına olanak tanır. Detaylı harita görünümü ve filtreleme seçenekleri ile en uygun şarj noktasını haritada bulmak artık çok kolay.

Akıllı Seyahat Planlama:
Voltla ile tüm marka şarj istasyonlarını görebilir, favori şarj istasyonuna rota oluşturabilir ve aracını güvenle şarj edebilirler! Voltla, şarj rehberinizdir. 

Şarj ve Ödeme Başlatma:
Voltla'nın on binlerce kullanıcısı şarj başlatma ve sonlandırma işlemlerini tek Voltla üzerinden güvenle yapabilirler.

Gerçek Zamanlı Güncellemeler: Kullanıcılar, şarj istasyonlarının mevcut durumunu gerçek zamanlı olarak görüntüleyebilirler. Bu özellik sayesinde dolu veya boş olan şarj istasyonlarını önceden öğrenerek zamandan tasarruf edebilirler.

Favori Şarj İstasyonu Noktaları: Kullanıcılar, sık kullandıkları veya tercih ettikleri eşarj istasyonlarını favorilere ekleyebilir ve daha sonra kolayca erişebilirler.

Filtre Kaydetme: Şarj istasyonlarını filtreleyebilir ve filtrelerinizi kaydedebilirsiniz. 

Kullanıcı Dostu Arayüz: Sadelik ve kullanım kolaylığı prensipleriyle tasarlanan Voltla, herkesin rahatlıkla kullanabileceği bir arayüz sunar.
Voltla ile elektrikli araç kullanıcıları artık şarj istasyonları konusunda endişe etmeden seyahat edebilirler. 

ELEKTRİKLİ ARAÇ ŞARJ İSTASYONLARINA AİT HANGİ BİLGİLERİ GÖREBİLİRİM?

• İstasyonun anlık meşguliyet bilgisi, istasyonun arızalı olup olmadığı bilgisi
• İstasyondaki soketlerin tipleri, enerji güçleri ve fiyat bilgisi

Realtime traffic information anytime & anywhere with İBB CepTrafik!

You can access realtime information via your mobile phone at any time with the İBBCepTrafik application (service of the Istanbul Metropolitan Municipality). İBBCepTrafik is an application that allows you to get realtime information with traffic cameras and heat map developed by Istanbul Metropolitan Municipality. You can access speed information received from traffic sensors of Istanbul Metropolitan Municipality, traffic camera images and traffic announcements published by the Transportation Management Center with this application.

You can make traffic-related notifications, share your opinions and suggestions through the application. For further information please contact us via uym@ibb.gov.tr 

In İBBCepTrafik application, traffic camera images are shown with 3 pictures that are played sequentially and changed every minute in order to minimize the internet traffic of users. You can add cameras and car parks to your favorite lists for the ones that you use frequently.

You need to zoom in/out on the map to see traffic sensors, more cameras, signalized junctions, charging stations, Isbike or car parks.

You can use the application over wireless and mobile operators. Data traffic that will occur during the usage of the application through operators may be deducted from your internet package or may be charged by your operators if you do not have an internet package. Make sure you are using the latest version

developer: Changsha Duyou Network Technology Co., Ltd
description:
Speedometer GPS: Speed ​​Monitor is a high-precision GPS speedometer that integrates speed monitoring, trip recording, HUD head-up display, speeding reminder and other functions. It provides real-time and accurate speed tracking and navigation assistance for drivers, cyclists, runners and outdoor explorers. Whether it is daily commuting, long-distance travel, or racing competition, this Speedometer app is your ideal choice!

Core functions

Accurate GPS speed measurement

Relying on high-precision GPS technology, it displays the current speed, average speed, and maximum speed in real time to ensure accurate speed measurement. Supports kilometer/hour (km/h) and mile/hour (mph) two unit switching.

Smart speeding alarm

Set a personalized speed limit value. Once the speed is exceeded, the application will issue an alarm to remind you, effectively preventing speeding and helping you drive safely. And it supports 4 preset speed limits, which can be switched with a single click, allowing you to operate more safely while driving!

HUD head-up display mode

After enabling HUD mode, place the phone under the windshield to project the speed information onto the windshield, making night driving safer.

Driving data record

Automatically record detailed data such as travel time, driving distance, stay time, altitude, etc. Allowing you to easily view historical travel data or share it.

Built-in map

The built-in map can display the current location in real time and draw the driving trajectory to prevent getting lost.

Picture-in-Picture Mode (PiP)

Enable Picture-in-Picture (PiP) mode to view speed information in real time while using other applications.
Suitable for scenarios such as navigation and music playback, so that speed measurement no longer affects other operations.
The window size and position can be adjusted to ensure the best visual experience while driving.

Altimeter & Altitude Measurement

Built-in accurate altitude measurement function, real-time monitoring of current altitude, suitable for mountain driving, cycling and outdoor adventures.

Speedometer helps you drive safely, accurately measure speed, and avoid speeding tickets! Download now to experience professional speed measurement service!

Free features:

The following core features are available without a subscription:

Real-time speed measurement

Remaining mileage statistics

Set maximum speed limit

Subscription features (premium features):

Unlock the full feature experience and obtain access through subscription:

Head-up display (HUD) mode

Picture-in-picture (PIP) mode

Map navigation integration

Driving data recording and statistics

Change speed dashboard style

Automatic renewal terms

Subscriptions will be charged to your iTunes account. Payment will be charged to the account immediately after confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions will automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period. The account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period, and the renewal amount will be determined. Users can manage or cancel subscriptions in "Settings" > "Apple ID" > "Subscriptions". After the free trial (if any) ends, the system will automatically start the subscription according to the selected plan unless canceled in advance.

Privacy Policy: https://sites.google.com/view/duyou-privacy-policy
Terms: https://sites.google.com/view/duyou-terms
